#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:1
msgid "模拟实盘交易——CLI 功能清单"
msgstr "Simulieren Sie echten Handel – CLI"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:3
msgid ""
"本文从命令与能力清单角度说明 CLI 中的模拟实盘功能。   如需按步骤操作，请阅读 `tutorials/8-live-trade-risk-and-"
"broker-walkthrough.md`。"
msgstr ""
"Auf dieser Seite wird der simulierte Live-Handel in der CLI aus der "
"Perspektive der Befehle und der Fähigkeitsliste beschrieben. Für eine "
"Schritt-für-Schritt-Anleitung lesen Sie „tutorials/8-live-trade-risk-and-"
"broker-walkthrough.md“."

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:6
msgid "0. 文档边界"
msgstr "0. Document Scope"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:8
msgid "本页是命令能力索引，不是逐步教程"
msgstr ""
"Bei dieser Seite handelt es sich um einen Befehlsfähigkeitsindex und nicht "
"um eine Schritt-für-Schritt-Anleitung"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:9
msgid "重点回答“有什么命令、看什么反馈、跳到哪里排查”"
msgstr ""
"Fokus: Welche Befehle existieren, welches Feedback zu lesen ist und wo "
"Fehler behoben werden müssen"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:11
msgid "1. 命令能力分组"
msgstr "1. Command Groups"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:13
msgid "**运行控制**：启动、暂停、恢复、结束"
msgstr "**Run control**: start, pause, resume, stop"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:14
msgid "**交易操作**：买入、卖出、撤单"
msgstr "**Trading**: buy, sell, cancel"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:15
msgid "**状态查询**：订单、成交、持仓、账户"
msgstr "**Status queries**: orders, fills, positions, account"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:16
msgid "**诊断与日志**：系统消息、错误提示、任务状态"
msgstr "**Diagnose und Protokolle**: Systemmeldungen, Fehler, Aufgabenstatus"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:18
msgid "2. 核心反馈语义"
msgstr "2. Core Feedback Semantics"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:20
msgid "拒单时可看到英文摘要（含 `rule_id` / `reason`）"
msgstr "Rejections show an English summary (with `rule_id` / `reason`)"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:21
msgid "分批成交状态更容易在查询结果中识别"
msgstr "Partial-fill status is easier to spot in query results"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:22
msgid "收盘后处理行为通过统一 Broker API 协调"
msgstr ""
"Die Handhabung nach dem Schließen wird über die einheitliche Broker-API "
"koordiniert"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:24
msgid "2.1 手工下单的订单类型语义（buy/sell）"
msgstr "2.1 Manual Order Types (buy/sell)"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:26
msgid "`buy/sell ... -p 正数`：按**限价单**提交（`order_type='limit'`）"
msgstr ""
"``buy/sell ... -p <positive>``: submit a **limit** order "
"(``order_type='limit'``)"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:27
msgid ""
"`buy/sell ...`（不带 `-p`）或 `-p 0`：按**市价单**提交（`order_type='market'`），CLI "
"会在下单前使用最新实时价补齐价格字段"
msgstr ""
"„kaufen/verkaufen ...“ ohne „-p“ oder mit „-p 0“: Senden Sie eine "
"**Markt**-Order (``order_type='market'``); CLI füllt den Preis vor der "
"Übermittlung aus dem neuesten Live-Angebot aus"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:29
msgid "在 `SimulatorBroker` 中，撮合判定的关键差异如下："
msgstr "In ``SimulatorBroker``, key matching differences are:"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "订单类型"
msgstr "Order type"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "主要成交条件（简化）"
msgstr "Main fill condition (simplified)"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "`limit` 限价单"
msgstr "``limit`` (limit order)"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "卖单：实时价 `>=` 挂卖价（含偏差）；买单：实时价 `<=` 挂买价（含偏差）"
msgstr ""
"Sell: live price ``>=`` limit sell (with tolerance); buy: live price ``<=`` "
"limit buy (with tolerance)"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "`market` 市价单"
msgstr "``market`` (market order)"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "实时涨跌幅位于非涨跌停区间时优先按市价撮合；若接近涨跌停，成交概率显著下降"
msgstr ""
"Bevorzugen Sie die Marktfüllung, wenn der Preis nicht in der Nähe des "
"oberen/unten-Limits liegt; Füllwahrscheinlichkeit sinkt in die Nähe der "
"Grenzen"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:36
msgid "示例（用户可见反馈）："
msgstr "Example (user-visible feedback):"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:42
msgid "3. 快速问题分流（CLI 视角）"
msgstr "3. Quick Triage (CLI View)"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:44
msgid "下单后没有订单记录：优先检查风控拒单提示"
msgstr "No order after submit: check risk rejection messages first"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:45
msgid "有订单但无成交：检查 broker 回报与行情条件"
msgstr ""
"Auftrag, aber keine Ausführung: Überprüfen Sie die Brokerberichte und die "
"Marktbedingungen"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:46
msgid "状态长时间不变：检查回报是否持续到达"
msgstr "Status stuck: check whether fill reports keep arriving"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md:48
msgid "4. 命令-文档映射"
msgstr "4. Command–Document Map"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "关注点"
msgstr "Concern"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "先看哪里"
msgstr "Check First"

#: ../../source/references/5-simulate-operation-in-CLI.md
msgid "运行是否配置正确"
msgstr "Run configuration correct"

